家烤箱的不同,烘烤時間可做調整。"},{"pid":"ad10bf6798c6e1e63dbd7822fef8f1689807b320","tid":724801,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b926ee1476526b0dfe5f6d65e2795ae8cb54c373","tid":724801,"uid":59570,"like":195,"dislike":2,"score":193,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:09:02.000Z","msg":"睇到個標題未click 入黎已經諗緊教你邊到整mon 好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T09:51:43.000Z","msg":"見到手機台就知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6442111f8f7ecad8359b6dcbb97cce4da3c7563","tid":724801,"uid":18366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:03:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a247e3d6d5ffd0e6cd61e316ef4b50844612db79","tid":724801,"uid":143762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:07:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"739e5ae8e311f13a48289ecd5f8ec4cad6245246","tid":724801,"uid":44711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"比少少新意好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a6e47179301c015a7c555271008f549c38e47b","tid":724801,"uid":29621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:19:13.000Z","msg":"深水埗鴨記中間有個後生仔整電話"},{"pid":"848b02bec8c03afdd0fbfe3ca9577e44b0c01ac1","tid":724801,"uid":29621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:19:39.000Z","msg":"不過呢D潮文<br />\n第一個做就好笑"},{"pid":"54b8de9cbcdf9f498e00f2158299dd59c4c38ff7","tid":724801,"uid":144279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:49:55.000Z","msg":"已經唔好笑了"},{"pid":"50e199d8b30db41e869b451f32bdb96df9165128","tid":724801,"uid":114275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:52:22.000Z","msg":"連登仔 爭氣 d <br />\n<br />\n見到呢 d 回帶 post 負個皮 block 9 樓主啦<br />\n<br />\n成日舊文當新 gag 連登邊有進步"},{"pid":"e2af7a5c351fb00c964e0ada65c1c72c108810b5","tid":724801,"uid":192078,"like":0,"d